### 8.2 Code Splitting & Bundle Audit
- [ ] Lazy-load: AI Studio, Governance, Insights, About, NotFound
- [ ] Confirm only 1 GSAP import (Act 2) ‚Äî not spreading GSAP across components
- [ ] Run `bun run build` and check chunk sizes; if any chunk > 200KB, split further
- [ ] Use `vite-bundle-visualizer` to inspect: `bun add -d vite-bundle-visualizer`

### 8.3 Core Web Vitals (CWV)
- [ ] LCP: ensure hero H1 and above-fold image have `fetchpriority="high"` if applicable
- [ ] CLS: verify all lazy-loaded images have reserved space
- [ ] INP: avoid long tasks during scroll events; debounce Observer callbacks if needed
