- [ ] Accordion (mobile nav): Enter/Space to toggle, aria-expanded, aria-controls
- [ ] Forms: every input has a `<label>` (not placeholder-only), error messages with `role="alert"`
- [ ] Breadcrumb: `nav aria-label="Breadcrumb"` + `aria-current="page"` on last item
- [ ] All icon-only buttons: `aria-label` describing action
- [ ] Color contrast: pulse-500 (#ff7a66) on white ‚Äî verify contrast ratio ‚â• 4.5:1; adjust shade if needed
- [ ] Images: meaningful `alt` text; decorative images use `alt=""`

