## Risk & Complexity Notes

### üî¥ High Complexity

| Area | Risk | Mitigation |
|---|---|---|
| **GSAP ScrollTrigger (Act 2)** | Pin + release must feel native, not jarring; breaks in reduced motion if not handled | Implement reduced motion fallback first; test GSAP last; add "Skip scene" button |
| **Mega Menu keyboard accessibility** | Focus trap, Escape behavior, arrow key nav are complex in custom menus | Use shadcn `NavigationMenu` as base ‚Äî Radix handles a11y primitives; test thoroughly |
| **IntersectionObserver + hash sync** | Race conditions if multiple acts intersect simultaneously; hash changes can cause scroll jumps | Use `history.replaceState` (not `location.hash =`); debounce observer callback |
| **Act 2 mini mapper + GSAP pin together** | Form interaction inside a pinned scene is fragile | Ensure pin releases before/after form interaction; test at multiple viewport sizes |

### üü° Medium Complexity

| Area | Risk | Mitigation |
|---|---|---|
| **dvh units in Hero** | `100dvh` not supported in all older browsers | Add `100vh` fallback: `min-height: 100vh; min-height: 100dvh` |
| **pulse-500 color contrast** | `#ff7a66` on white = ~2.9:1 ‚Äî fails WCAG AA for normal text | Use pulse-500 for large text/UI only; use `pulse-700` or darker shade for text on light bg |
| **Opportunity Mapper mock generator** | Output must feel plausible and deterministic enough for demos | Map inputs to pre-written output templates by industry/pain combination |
| **Code splitting lazy boundaries** | React.lazy + Suspense with router: error boundaries needed | Wrap each lazy route in `<ErrorBoundary>` + `<Suspense>` |
| **Service slugs** | Slug in URL (`/services/knowledge-ai-rag`) must match exactly | Derive slug from service name in data file; use consistent kebab-case slugging helper |

### üü¢ Performance Risks

| Risk | Priority | Note |
|---|---|---|
| GSAP bundle size (~100KB) | Medium | Imported only in Act 2 component; lazy import if possible |
| Framer Motion full bundle | Medium | Import only needed components: `motion`, `AnimatePresence` ‚Äî not entire lib |
| No CLS on image-heavy cards | High | Always set `width`/`height` or `aspect-ratio` on `<img>` and video containers |
| Hero LCP | High | H1 text is LCP candidate ‚Äî ensure font loads early (preconnect to Google Fonts) |

### ‚ôø Accessibility Risks

| Risk | Priority | Note |
|---|---|---|
| Reduced motion not covering all animations | Critical | Every animation site must be gated by `useReducedMotion` hook |
| Form error announcements | High | Use `role="alert"` or `aria-live="polite"` on error containers |
| Mega menu focus trap escape | High | Pressing Escape must return focus to the "Services" trigger button |
| Icon-only buttons without labels | Medium | Audit: any button using only an SVG icon needs `aria-label` |
| Color-only state indicators | Medium | Active nav link must not rely solely on color ‚Äî add underline, bold, or other indicator |
